From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dynamic Devices <support@dynamicdevices.co.uk>
Date: Sun, 31 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] arm: dts: imx95: add imx95-15x15-frdm.dtb to build list

u-boot-fio imx-2024.04 ships imx95-15x15-evk.dts but not the FRDM board
tree. meta-dynamicdevices-bsp ships imx95-15x15-frdm.dts via SRC_URI subdir=
and lists the DTB here so do_compile can build it.
---
 arch/arm/dts/Makefile | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/dts/Makefile b/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
index 1111111111..2222222222 100644
--- a/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm/dts/Makefile
@@ -1184,6 +1184,7 @@ dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_IMX9) += \
 
 dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_IMX9) += \
 	imx95-15x15-evk.dtb \
+	imx95-15x15-frdm.dtb \
 	imx95-19x19-evk.dtb \
 	imx95-19x19-verdin.dtb \
 	imx91-11x11-evk.dtb \
